{"tid":2151670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支那01】環時：美粗暴開拆中國駐聯國代表團所訂傢俱　中方將採取對等措施","createTime":"2020-08-11T13:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:45:17.000Z","uid":51665,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d3d37ef9ac3dc5c1575a55012cd605c9616ce9","tid":2151670,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"內地官媒《環球時報》今天（11日）晚間發文稱，美方早前粗暴開拆查驗了中國駐聯合國代表團訂購的一批總共60件的傢俱（公務用品），嚴重違反國際慣例。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》稱，中方將對美方採取對等措施是可以預期的。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，近期，中國常駐聯合國代表團訂購了60件傢俱(主要為梳化、椅子、茶几等)。為辦理清關手續，常駐團於6月30日按美方要求提交了申請材料。因未獲答覆，常駐團於7月13日催促美使團辦紐約辦公室儘快辦理，該辦當日答覆稱，到港集裝箱正在接受檢查，檢查完成後才能批復清關申請，常駐團隨即向美方提出嚴正交涉，強調此批貨物系中方公務用品，且中方已按美方要求履行清關手續，美開拆查驗的做法不符合國際慣例。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《環時》指，經中方反復催詢，美使團辦終於批復常駐團清關申請，清關代理於7月23日將傢俱送抵常駐團，此時已距中方按美方要求提交申請材料將近一個月；而經檢查發現，此次集裝箱鉛封已被替換，貨物中有12件外包裝被明顯撕壞並貼上美方檢驗標識。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進：美國存心找茬，像個「外交流氓」<br />\n<br />\n《環時》指，美方開拆查驗中方外交使團公務用品的做法粗暴蠻橫，顯然不符合國際慣例，損害中美互信與合作，這是蓄意製造麻煩和障礙，根據國際慣例，中方有權採取對等措施。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》總編胡錫進則在微博對此發文稱，美方這是「存心找茬」，在對華問題上頻頻表現得像一個「外交流氓」。胡錫進說，對等原則是外交關係的基石，幾輪交手，中方堅守這一原則的決心和能力都已經明確無誤，如果美國的確是個文明國家，就請他們停止各種無賴操作，回歸到大國外交的應有禮數上來。<br />\n<br />\n吹咩！拆返人吖笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead1425c6f6685ae281072a78b8b5fc9cb6fd08d","tid":2151670,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"點反制<br />\n斬幾舊木當反制左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d7d0af08ea284bb2dc8d7b37c426d34fda1e24","tid":2151670,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsWs6kc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbsWs6kc.gif&h=9c7da371&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b10a939daf268f0bba8fc1ac4180a7914483653","tid":2151670,"uid":82359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"唔拆點check呀，即係你話ok就ok 呀<br />\n咁我洗乜要海關呀"},{"pid":"75cd217910f69968ccad0f9653d2ee6985aae070","tid":2151670,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=2338bc3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"b60a4fb93b6c8230be7a2dca281529c6a2cad01b","tid":2151670,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"[有圖] 陳敏之呢對屌西腳真係可以奶成晚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2151673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2151673</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27e95940274fbcce6b7ed37ff31021ac79b91eca","tid":2151670,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時先屌侵侵高大過習敗敗係辱華？"},{"pid":"48a7d52d9b4b78029c5ffc24d56e2c63cf0935f3","tid":2151670,"uid":266336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85LBffm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85LBffm.gif&h=bd965202&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSe6CtD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSe6CtD.gif&h=1b19809b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ea30d0d90d55b0964deddb749ee4170d1283a7d","tid":2151670,"uid